WEBVTT

01:26.250 --> 01:35.000
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.259 --> 01:37.950
[Episode 22]

01:41.930 --> 01:43.500
Seems you're catching on.

01:44.479 --> 01:46.009
As long as you want to learn,

01:46.509 --> 01:48.400
I will teach you

01:48.430 --> 01:50.360
everything without reservation.

01:51.150 --> 01:52.050
Mr. Cao,

01:52.450 --> 01:53.009
I'm here.

01:56.770 --> 01:58.140
Why are you early?

02:00.700 --> 02:01.360
Please carry on.

02:01.360 --> 02:02.220
I'll come back later.

02:02.220 --> 02:02.810
No, no.

02:02.840 --> 02:06.300
[Spirits Soaring High]

02:02.930 --> 02:03.750
Well,

02:03.980 --> 02:05.450
Uncle, I'll come back tomorrow.

02:05.450 --> 02:06.760
You do your business first.

02:06.760 --> 02:07.150
Okay.

02:12.310 --> 02:13.130
Great acting.

02:18.190 --> 02:18.870
It's fine.

02:19.870 --> 02:20.750
He's my nephew.

02:27.460 --> 02:28.200
Thanks.

02:40.320 --> 02:41.520
Let me give you an update.

02:41.520 --> 02:43.630
I've been doing transportation lately.

02:43.630 --> 02:44.470
It's legal.

02:45.090 --> 02:47.180
I bring in beef and mutton
from Inner Mongolia,

02:47.180 --> 02:49.140
and supply them to restaurants.

02:49.340 --> 02:50.579
I keep some for myself,

02:50.579 --> 02:51.870
and also run a barbecue stall.

02:51.870 --> 02:52.870
Isn't that great?

02:53.720 --> 02:55.250
Put in a good word for me with your sis.

02:55.250 --> 02:55.990
No problem.

02:56.650 --> 02:58.650
What about your construction team?

03:00.500 --> 03:02.710
There's less work than before.

03:03.180 --> 03:03.980
That won't do.

03:05.090 --> 03:06.290
You have to work hard.

03:06.460 --> 03:07.750
Work your tail off.

03:08.800 --> 03:09.500
I'll see when my sis

03:09.500 --> 03:10.760
will let you come back.

03:10.780 --> 03:11.310
Shengli.

03:12.360 --> 03:13.590
I'm being honest with you.

03:13.590 --> 03:15.320
Why are you being so sarcastic?

03:16.400 --> 03:17.300
Surviving out here

03:17.300 --> 03:19.130
isn't like being a big screenwriter.

03:19.130 --> 03:21.240
You can't be dead broke one night,

03:21.310 --> 03:22.540
and rich the next...

03:22.970 --> 03:23.400
Wait.

03:24.740 --> 03:26.270
What's the meaning of this?

03:26.910 --> 03:28.370
I-It's...

03:28.620 --> 03:29.430
It's not that easy?

03:29.430 --> 03:30.490
It's not that easy?

03:31.900 --> 03:33.630
I think it's quite easy for you.

03:34.520 --> 03:35.130
You really

03:35.410 --> 03:36.860
don't ever want to go back, do you?

03:36.860 --> 03:39.060
Last time you were crying your eyes out,

03:39.240 --> 03:40.829
saying how much you missed your daughter,

03:40.829 --> 03:42.490
and how much you missed my sis.

03:43.060 --> 03:44.810
It's a pity you're not an actor.

03:49.030 --> 03:51.070
Can you spare a thought for me?

03:51.900 --> 03:53.430
You think I like doing this?

03:54.079 --> 03:55.300
People yell in my face every day.

03:55.300 --> 03:56.020
You think I like that?

03:56.020 --> 03:57.370
I'm just trying to make some money

03:57.370 --> 03:58.560
to pay off the debt.

03:58.620 --> 03:59.280
Once I pay off the debt,

03:59.280 --> 04:00.940
I'll stop doing this for sure.

04:01.150 --> 04:01.960
I swear to you.

04:02.470 --> 04:04.530
If I do this again, I'm a son of a bitch.

04:08.620 --> 04:10.960
You'll stop once the debt is paid?

04:11.520 --> 04:12.890
I definitely will.

04:13.240 --> 04:14.300
It's already paid.

04:15.900 --> 04:17.209
Mr. Big Screenwriter.

04:17.310 --> 04:18.060
The debt is paid

04:18.060 --> 04:18.930
just because you said so?

04:18.930 --> 04:19.560
My sis sold

04:19.560 --> 04:21.600
the house her dad left her.

04:29.680 --> 04:30.390
She originally didn't want me

04:30.390 --> 04:31.420
to tell you this.

04:44.250 --> 04:45.580
At 10:00 a.m. tomorrow,

04:45.720 --> 04:47.920
she will be waiting for you at the store.

04:59.650 --> 05:01.790
[CHUN LAI JIE]

05:17.860 --> 05:21.810
I've searched for you
over thousands of miles.

05:23.120 --> 05:26.540
But you don't even care.

05:30.040 --> 05:34.190
You don't seem to be in my dreams.

05:35.520 --> 05:39.570
But in my dreams, you are my only one.

05:53.810 --> 05:54.780
Are you hungry?

05:58.000 --> 05:59.730
I'll make you a bowl of noodles.

06:15.570 --> 06:18.730
[Endeavor]

06:17.770 --> 06:18.500
Out of money?

06:21.800 --> 06:27.260
[Endeavor]

06:25.040 --> 06:27.640
Did you really split 20-80
with Zhuang Zhuang?

06:28.630 --> 06:30.280
No, 50-50.

06:31.420 --> 06:33.360
Before Zhuang Zhuang
took classes last year,

06:33.360 --> 06:34.770
she paid the teacher a large amount

06:34.770 --> 06:35.970
of owed tuition fees.

06:35.970 --> 06:39.540
[Endeavor]

06:36.430 --> 06:38.090
She also sent some money home,

06:38.240 --> 06:39.500
so she doesn't have much left.

06:39.500 --> 06:40.560
I'm about the same.

06:40.920 --> 06:42.460
I sent some home,

06:42.870 --> 06:43.800
recorded a song,

06:43.950 --> 06:45.640
and paid half a year's rent.

06:46.800 --> 06:48.159
If we don't make money
for another 2 months,

06:48.159 --> 06:49.930
I'll be living a hard life
with you, buddy.

06:49.930 --> 06:50.560
Save it.

06:50.630 --> 06:52.170
Don't live a hard life with me.

06:52.170 --> 06:55.400
[Endeavor]

06:52.480 --> 06:55.280
You can't handle it.

06:58.310 --> 06:59.540
We can't go on like this.

06:59.540 --> 07:00.870
We need to think of a way.

07:01.190 --> 07:02.130
What way?

07:02.360 --> 07:04.240
There's no ready work for us to do.

07:05.390 --> 07:06.430
There is a way.

07:14.360 --> 07:15.090
Look for him.

07:21.000 --> 07:22.090
You call him.

07:23.220 --> 07:25.360
I care about my pride.

07:28.750 --> 07:30.880
Pride? But you're childhood friends.

07:31.690 --> 07:32.450
Care about your pride?

07:32.450 --> 07:34.120
If you care about pride,
don't try to make money.

07:34.120 --> 07:36.450
Just pretend he's your childhood friend.

07:36.450 --> 07:37.909
Just invite him to dinner.

07:37.920 --> 07:39.520
We'll talk when he gets here.

07:41.180 --> 07:42.909
Stop pressing the calculator.

07:43.360 --> 07:44.159
It's bad luck.

07:49.900 --> 07:51.980
The signal is bad in this basement.

07:53.770 --> 07:54.430
I haven't played

07:54.430 --> 07:55.630
that thing for years.

07:55.930 --> 07:57.659
I'm busy with other things now.

07:58.250 --> 07:59.620
Ask someone else.

08:00.690 --> 08:01.930
No, I'm really

08:01.930 --> 08:03.460
busy with other things now.

08:03.890 --> 08:04.890
I don't have time.

08:05.570 --> 08:06.060
Okay.

08:06.100 --> 08:07.300
I'll call you back later.

08:07.300 --> 08:08.060
I'm hanging up.

08:08.060 --> 08:09.520
Thank you, Director Wang.

08:10.810 --> 08:12.750
-What a waste of my phone bill.
-Slow down.

08:12.750 --> 08:15.270
You are Liangliang's
childhood friend, right?

08:15.270 --> 08:16.100
Look at him,

08:16.540 --> 08:18.500
young and promising.

08:19.930 --> 08:21.000
Ma Xiaojun.

08:21.360 --> 08:23.020
This is Guo Zongbao, an actor.

08:23.220 --> 08:24.040
Hello.

08:24.190 --> 08:25.100
An actor?

08:25.100 --> 08:25.740
Actor, yes.

08:25.740 --> 08:27.200
A guest actor. I had lines.

08:28.390 --> 08:30.060
I'm meeting a star.

08:30.510 --> 08:31.860
I was just saying you looked a bit...

08:31.860 --> 08:33.049
a bit familiar.
You must have starred in...

08:33.049 --> 08:33.530
Really?

08:34.740 --> 08:37.360
Starred in...

08:38.870 --> 08:39.799
S-Starred in...

08:40.120 --> 08:41.000
I brought you guys

08:41.000 --> 08:41.850
some tea,

08:42.000 --> 08:43.289
pastries, and snacks.

08:43.600 --> 08:44.460
Let me think about it.

08:44.460 --> 08:45.310
Have a seat.

08:45.790 --> 08:47.020
Why haven't you

08:47.360 --> 08:48.860
moved to another place yet?

08:48.860 --> 08:50.630
It's cozy here.

08:50.740 --> 08:52.200
We are used to living here.

08:52.910 --> 08:54.240
Why did you call me here?

08:57.370 --> 08:58.170
To make money.

08:58.530 --> 09:00.130
Didn't we just make a sum of money?

09:00.130 --> 09:01.430
We kind of spent

09:01.460 --> 09:03.300
all the money we made before.

09:03.740 --> 09:05.130
What did you do? You spent it so quickly.

09:05.130 --> 09:07.120
We had to spend money on everything.

09:07.120 --> 09:08.480
So it's gone.

09:08.790 --> 09:10.790
If you need money, come to Mr. Lucky.

09:11.980 --> 09:13.460
Find Lucky, get lucky.

09:14.000 --> 09:15.800
You've come to the right person.

09:16.720 --> 09:18.180
But my luck is bad now, too.

09:19.270 --> 09:20.600
It's not the season yet.

09:20.700 --> 09:21.770
In China and Russia...

09:21.770 --> 09:23.030
You see, it's the off-season now.

09:23.030 --> 09:24.030
It has to be colder.

09:24.030 --> 09:25.320
Now I mainly

09:25.440 --> 09:28.000
do some middleman work
for the surrounding factories

09:28.000 --> 09:29.120
to make some money.

09:29.360 --> 09:31.010
But it's a one-person job.

09:33.410 --> 09:35.010
You guys gotta think of a way.

09:35.460 --> 09:36.390
This economy...

09:39.320 --> 09:40.110
This...

09:40.910 --> 09:43.170
Do you know how expensive a phone call is?

09:45.600 --> 09:48.500
You, a screenwriter...

09:49.790 --> 09:50.940
An actor...

09:52.000 --> 09:52.620
A...

09:54.030 --> 09:55.090
Saxophone player.

09:55.320 --> 09:56.380
Saxophone player.

10:00.530 --> 10:01.330
Wait a minute.

10:01.360 --> 10:01.910
What's the matter?

10:01.910 --> 10:02.910
No, wait a minute.

10:10.180 --> 10:11.860
Director. Director Wang, it's me.

10:11.860 --> 10:12.750
Lucky Ma.

10:13.240 --> 10:13.750
Yes.

10:13.750 --> 10:15.290
What was the matter you mentioned before?

10:15.290 --> 10:16.690
Could you say that again?

10:16.700 --> 10:18.370
Yes, what do you need?

10:19.000 --> 10:20.820
You're looking for a band?

10:24.210 --> 10:26.010
Okay, I'll arrange it for you.

10:26.080 --> 10:27.410
I'll reply to you later.

10:27.700 --> 10:28.560
I'm hanging up.

10:29.330 --> 10:30.850
Hey, exactly 59 seconds.

10:32.400 --> 10:34.170
Let's do band gigs.

10:34.270 --> 10:35.360
No problem.

10:35.460 --> 10:37.550
What's a gig?

10:37.620 --> 10:38.250
A gig is when

10:38.250 --> 10:40.240
singers and dancers

10:40.460 --> 10:41.260
come together

10:41.270 --> 10:43.010
to form a moving band.

10:43.120 --> 10:44.650
You'll travel from city to city to perform

10:44.650 --> 10:46.260
at factory parties,

10:46.290 --> 10:48.290
celebrations,

10:48.530 --> 10:50.580
weddings, funerals,

10:50.630 --> 10:51.390
and baby showers.

10:51.390 --> 10:52.930
You perform place by place,

10:53.410 --> 10:54.410
sing place by place,

10:54.410 --> 10:55.340
make money place by place,

10:55.340 --> 10:56.360
and share the money show by show.

10:56.360 --> 10:57.580
It's perfect for us.

10:58.770 --> 10:59.530
That works.

10:59.600 --> 11:00.050
Sounds good.

11:00.050 --> 11:00.390
This will work.

11:00.390 --> 11:00.920
Exactly.

11:01.010 --> 11:02.150
Don't you all have specialties?

11:02.150 --> 11:03.120
Aren't you playing the...

11:03.120 --> 11:03.780
Saxophone.

11:03.820 --> 11:04.080
Yes.

11:04.100 --> 11:05.030
I remember when you were young,

11:05.030 --> 11:05.550
you could play the...

11:05.550 --> 11:06.220
Guitar.

11:06.910 --> 11:08.130
And the young lady can...

11:08.130 --> 11:08.650
Sing.

11:09.890 --> 11:10.510
Bro, what about you?

11:10.510 --> 11:11.550
I'm an actor.

11:11.630 --> 11:13.160
I can also sing Yu Opera.

11:13.850 --> 11:18.470
Big Brother Liu's words are...

11:18.600 --> 11:19.790
-Bro.
-It’s too...

11:19.820 --> 11:20.770
Your voice cracked.

11:20.770 --> 11:21.270
Is it okay?

11:21.270 --> 11:22.410
I think when we get to the right place,

11:22.410 --> 11:23.870
you might be loved

11:23.910 --> 11:25.840
by middle-aged and elderly women.

11:25.870 --> 11:27.060
Sounds good.

11:27.340 --> 11:29.200
Doesn't Ranran know how to dance?

11:29.200 --> 11:30.000
Don't bother her.

11:30.000 --> 11:31.120
She's a big star now.

11:31.120 --> 11:32.360
She can't go gigging with us.

11:32.360 --> 11:33.320
Come on.

11:34.000 --> 11:35.250
Let Zhuang Zhuang ask her.

11:35.250 --> 11:36.050
If she is free,

11:36.050 --> 11:36.910
she can join us.

11:36.960 --> 11:38.270
We can all make money together.

11:38.270 --> 11:39.360
Let's do it together.

11:39.360 --> 11:40.690
What are you going to do?

11:41.010 --> 11:42.340
Well, if all else fails, I can

11:42.340 --> 11:43.290
write a sketch for them.

11:43.290 --> 11:44.020
Sounds good.

11:44.290 --> 11:45.150
I think you are quite smart.

11:45.150 --> 11:47.560
Why don't you be in charge of

11:47.580 --> 11:48.240
contact matters?

11:48.240 --> 11:49.720
How about being the general agent?

11:49.720 --> 11:50.830
Sure.

11:51.510 --> 11:52.570
That's great.

11:52.740 --> 11:53.430
Right?

11:53.500 --> 11:55.270
Now we have a full team, don't we?

11:55.270 --> 11:56.670
We've got everything...

11:57.200 --> 11:59.100
All ready now.

11:59.170 --> 11:59.750
How great is that?

11:59.750 --> 12:00.640
Ma Xiaojun

12:00.820 --> 12:02.080
has never dropped the ball

12:02.080 --> 12:03.480
since we were kids.

12:03.960 --> 12:04.570
I know.

12:04.790 --> 12:05.850
Really.

12:06.050 --> 12:07.550
We've been through life and death together

12:07.550 --> 12:09.470
in Russia, after all.

12:09.500 --> 12:10.270
Yes, yes.

12:12.510 --> 12:13.500
Our performance group

12:13.500 --> 12:14.960
needs a name, right?

12:16.580 --> 12:17.250
You tell me.

12:17.670 --> 12:18.730
Let me think of one.

12:19.720 --> 12:20.980
It should be called...

12:21.320 --> 12:22.680
Let's call it...

12:23.910 --> 12:25.290
I remember what you acted in!

12:25.290 --> 12:25.750
What?

12:25.820 --> 12:27.080
I suddenly remembered it.

12:27.080 --> 12:28.070
You acted in...

12:28.200 --> 12:29.780
He acted in that thing...

12:29.890 --> 12:31.280
Called...

12:31.360 --> 12:32.600
"Transformers." No.

12:33.010 --> 12:34.610
"Plain Ranger Team," right?

12:34.620 --> 12:35.270
Yes!

12:35.360 --> 12:36.080
Yes!

12:36.150 --> 12:37.240
He played that traitor

12:37.240 --> 12:38.270
with the middle-part hair.

12:38.270 --> 12:39.270
I remember it so clearly.

12:39.270 --> 12:40.920
No, I wasn't the traitor.

12:41.080 --> 12:43.400
I played the squad leader!

12:43.510 --> 12:44.770
As soon as I yelled, "Charge"...

12:44.770 --> 12:45.550
Squad leader.

12:45.550 --> 12:46.720
A bunch of big stars

12:46.770 --> 12:48.370
rushed into the battle.

12:48.980 --> 12:50.740
Squad leader, right.

12:51.130 --> 12:52.510
You two should exchange contact info.

12:52.510 --> 12:53.550
I'll give you my business card.

12:53.550 --> 12:54.320
Write this...

12:54.320 --> 12:56.170
The new version of "Plain Ranger Team."

12:56.170 --> 12:57.790
I'll print you another business card

12:57.790 --> 12:58.790
for your performance group.

12:58.790 --> 12:59.390
Okay.

12:59.820 --> 13:00.770
Write down my cell phone number.

13:00.770 --> 13:01.290
It's fine.

13:01.290 --> 13:02.150
Write down my cell phone number.

13:02.150 --> 13:02.860
Write down my cell phone number.

13:02.860 --> 13:04.500
716... 716, 8888.

13:04.540 --> 13:06.000
Very easy to remember. Write it down.

13:06.000 --> 13:06.270
Okay.

13:06.270 --> 13:08.360
-I’ll get you guys a cell phone next time.
-No rush.

13:08.360 --> 13:09.560
Don't laugh, really.

13:10.240 --> 13:11.170
You know, I...

13:12.050 --> 13:13.850
Traveled from Huzhou to Beijing

13:14.600 --> 13:16.620
just to be a good actress.

13:17.750 --> 13:19.220
But the whole world doesn't think

13:19.220 --> 13:20.340
I can be an actress.

13:20.840 --> 13:21.860
Even my mom doesn't think

13:21.860 --> 13:22.670
I can do it.

13:22.980 --> 13:24.710
But you are doing great now.

13:25.600 --> 13:26.370
And you are

13:26.370 --> 13:27.970
a good actress to begin with.

13:29.370 --> 13:30.140
Really?

13:31.650 --> 13:33.310
I'm starting to doubt myself.

13:34.270 --> 13:36.020
What's wrong, Shen Ranran?

13:36.910 --> 13:38.150
You need to be more confident.

13:38.150 --> 13:39.240
Look at how much effort you've put

13:39.240 --> 13:40.570
into acting.

13:40.770 --> 13:42.410
Practicing lines and pronunciation

13:42.410 --> 13:43.320
here every day.

13:43.650 --> 13:44.620
And you were

13:45.150 --> 13:46.810
running between sets, right?

13:47.100 --> 13:49.360
You were running between sets every day.

13:52.580 --> 13:54.210
So your recent show is done,

13:54.600 --> 13:56.060
are you shooting a new one?

14:00.510 --> 14:01.030
Zhuang,

14:02.980 --> 14:04.260
to tell you the truth,

14:06.440 --> 14:07.450
my previous role

14:07.580 --> 14:09.290
was recommended by Mr. Chu.

14:10.960 --> 14:11.530
I thought

14:11.580 --> 14:12.820
I got it on my own.

14:16.960 --> 14:18.490
Ever since that show ended,

14:19.770 --> 14:21.930
I’ve received many offers

14:21.960 --> 14:23.290
for movies and TV shows.

14:25.170 --> 14:26.510
At first, they were very serious

14:26.510 --> 14:28.510
about discussing the roles with me.

14:29.460 --> 14:30.340
But in the end,

14:31.530 --> 14:32.460
they all asked me

14:33.050 --> 14:34.780
if Mr. Chu could invest in them.

14:39.750 --> 14:40.500
Besides,

14:40.910 --> 14:42.510
everyone in my previous crew

14:43.390 --> 14:44.700
treated me very well.

14:45.240 --> 14:46.790
But I found it very strange,

14:47.410 --> 14:48.220
because it wasn't

14:48.220 --> 14:51.220
something a new actor should have.

14:52.510 --> 14:53.440
Does it mean that

14:54.340 --> 14:54.980
for the rest of my life,

14:54.980 --> 14:56.340
I have to rely on Mr. Chu

14:56.360 --> 14:57.860
to get roles?

14:59.360 --> 15:00.760
I am very grateful to him,

15:03.100 --> 15:05.100
and I cherish every opportunity.

15:07.700 --> 15:08.470
But I think

15:08.500 --> 15:10.630
I shouldn't keep going down this path.

15:12.360 --> 15:13.890
I understand what you mean.

15:17.510 --> 15:18.570
If something

15:19.000 --> 15:20.490
can make us happy,

15:20.620 --> 15:21.580
we will do it.

15:21.910 --> 15:23.170
If it makes us unhappy,

15:23.890 --> 15:26.150
then we should think about it carefully.

15:31.080 --> 15:33.410
Have you talked to Liangliang about this?

15:33.740 --> 15:34.290
No.

15:36.530 --> 15:37.470
He is

15:37.500 --> 15:39.240
a very simple and naive person.

15:40.650 --> 15:41.620
I don't want to talk to him

15:41.620 --> 15:44.350
about such complicated
and realistic problems.

15:51.580 --> 15:53.550
If you are not filming recently,

15:53.650 --> 15:54.050
do you want to

15:54.050 --> 15:55.780
go touring and gigging with us?

15:55.820 --> 15:57.620
A performance tour, basically.

15:57.740 --> 15:58.580
Mr. Xu, Guo,

15:58.600 --> 15:59.840
Liangliang, and I

15:59.960 --> 16:00.960
will all be there.

16:01.790 --> 16:02.450
I want to go.

16:05.630 --> 16:06.170
But...

16:07.670 --> 16:09.160
Before the New Year,

16:09.340 --> 16:11.500
Liangliang and I had
some misunderstandings.

16:11.500 --> 16:12.850
Would he want me to go?

16:12.890 --> 16:14.890
He was the one who asked me to ask you.

16:14.910 --> 16:16.970
He was afraid you wouldn't want to go.

16:17.500 --> 16:18.340
Really?

16:18.550 --> 16:19.150
Not at all.

16:22.480 --> 16:23.230
I want to go.

16:23.370 --> 16:25.170
I'm happy when I'm with you guys.

16:26.740 --> 16:27.400
It's a deal.

16:32.530 --> 16:33.030
Ranran.

16:34.480 --> 16:35.080
I am sorry.

16:39.700 --> 16:41.390
What a beautiful bouquet.

16:41.510 --> 16:42.650
I'll introduce you to a boyfriend later,

16:42.650 --> 16:44.110
so he can give you flowers.

16:47.940 --> 16:48.800
Sorry, Ranran.

16:49.550 --> 16:50.500
What are you doing?

16:50.500 --> 16:51.860
The flowers are withered
after waiting all morning.

16:51.860 --> 16:52.940
I'm spraying some water on them for you.

16:52.940 --> 16:54.290
I don't need you to do that.

16:54.290 --> 16:56.490
How can you bite the hand that feeds you?

16:56.740 --> 16:57.820
Who's biting

16:57.820 --> 16:58.820
what hand now?

16:58.890 --> 17:00.360
You're only assertive towards me.

17:00.360 --> 17:01.250
When you see Ranran later,

17:01.250 --> 17:02.320
you will wimp out immediately.

17:02.320 --> 17:03.120
Who's going to wimp out?

17:03.120 --> 17:04.460
I'll be like this when I see her, too.

17:04.460 --> 17:05.349
Ranran is back.

17:05.510 --> 17:07.180
You need to go back inside quickly.

17:07.180 --> 17:07.900
Ranran.

17:08.920 --> 17:09.980
She's really back.

17:10.050 --> 17:10.510
Go away.

17:13.160 --> 17:15.770
[Car Deposit]

17:14.310 --> 17:16.089
He's been waiting for you all morning.

17:16.089 --> 17:17.020
Hurry up. Hurry.

17:21.829 --> 17:26.470
[Car Deposit]

17:28.349 --> 17:29.000
I'm sorry.

17:30.380 --> 17:31.550
Sorry for what?

17:32.880 --> 17:34.140
You know how I am.

17:34.220 --> 17:35.290
I'm not easily offended

17:35.290 --> 17:36.200
by others' words.

17:36.200 --> 17:38.270
But I'm always offending

17:39.010 --> 17:40.760
others with my words.

17:41.680 --> 17:42.740
If you're unhappy,

17:46.110 --> 17:47.540
just hit me.

17:47.960 --> 17:49.020
Why would I hit you?

17:50.660 --> 17:51.640
To...

17:52.240 --> 17:52.880
Vent your anger.

17:52.880 --> 17:53.900
Hit me.

17:53.900 --> 17:55.170
I'm very soft here.

17:57.430 --> 18:04.340
[Car Deposit]

18:08.380 --> 18:09.180
Isn't it soft?

18:13.010 --> 18:13.610
Well...

18:16.050 --> 18:17.510
Our performance group

18:17.880 --> 18:18.810
is having dinner

18:19.980 --> 18:21.040
together tonight.

18:21.640 --> 18:22.610
You should come too.

18:22.610 --> 18:24.150
Why wouldn't I go to dinner?

18:24.740 --> 18:25.540
I'm going too.

18:27.080 --> 18:27.880
Wait a minute.

18:28.460 --> 18:28.940
Um.

18:31.030 --> 18:31.560
Flowers.

18:33.510 --> 18:34.160
I'm sorry.

18:45.810 --> 18:48.250
Today is the first meeting

18:48.530 --> 18:49.940
of our Singing Along the Way

18:49.940 --> 18:52.250
Art Troupe since its establishment.

18:52.550 --> 18:54.850
It has historical significance.

18:56.520 --> 18:57.080
Applaud.

18:59.330 --> 18:59.790
Nice.

19:00.160 --> 19:01.020
Now,

19:01.480 --> 19:03.970
please allow me to introduce

19:04.310 --> 19:06.280
our leader,

19:06.610 --> 19:10.180
General Manager Mr. Lucky Ma.

19:11.050 --> 19:12.380
Come on, say a few words.

19:12.500 --> 19:13.680
Say a few words.

19:14.460 --> 19:15.330
Look, he's shy.

19:15.440 --> 19:16.250
What are you talking about?

19:16.250 --> 19:17.050
Be confident.

19:17.610 --> 19:19.110
I am not a leader.

19:19.270 --> 19:22.220
I'm not a chairman

19:22.240 --> 19:22.740
or a general manager.

19:22.740 --> 19:23.330
No, no.

19:23.530 --> 19:25.380
I am just in charge of paving the way.

19:25.380 --> 19:25.880
To be exact,

19:25.880 --> 19:27.010
I am your lead horse,

19:27.160 --> 19:27.830
responsible for

19:27.830 --> 19:29.560
receiving some small business for you.

19:29.560 --> 19:30.400
Right? Right.

19:30.460 --> 19:31.180
But

19:32.770 --> 19:34.010
when it comes to real work,

19:34.010 --> 19:34.590
it still depends on

19:34.590 --> 19:35.700
all you artists present.

19:35.700 --> 19:36.160
Agreed.

19:37.140 --> 19:38.070
I will, I will...

19:38.530 --> 19:39.880
I'll stop here. Yeah.

19:39.940 --> 19:40.740
Say a few more words.

19:40.740 --> 19:41.140
No, no.

19:41.140 --> 19:42.080
Enough, enough.

19:42.110 --> 19:43.700
Why are you being so modest?

19:43.810 --> 19:44.590
I have never been a leader.

19:44.590 --> 19:46.050
I get nervous when I speak.

19:46.140 --> 19:46.980
My palms get all sweaty.

19:46.980 --> 19:47.580
All right.

19:48.350 --> 19:50.950
I will be responsible
for daily management,

19:51.180 --> 19:52.410
public relations,

19:52.500 --> 19:54.830
hosting, and MCing.

19:54.850 --> 19:55.570
I can do all that.

19:55.570 --> 19:56.740
Zhuang Zhuang can sing.

19:56.740 --> 19:57.070
Okay.

19:57.090 --> 19:58.100
Ranran can dance.

19:58.510 --> 19:59.620
As for Liangliang,

19:59.750 --> 20:01.060
he's multi-talented.

20:01.090 --> 20:03.070
He plays the saxophone, cucurbit flute,

20:03.070 --> 20:04.180
keyboard, guitar,

20:04.200 --> 20:05.830
and other instruments.

20:06.000 --> 20:06.860
How about this?

20:06.980 --> 20:08.500
I will be in charge of

20:09.550 --> 20:11.430
this band.

20:11.700 --> 20:14.230
I will be the captain of the band.

20:14.880 --> 20:16.940
There is no towering tree in society,

20:17.220 --> 20:19.610
I am Liangliang. Remember me.

20:20.200 --> 20:21.260
Thank you.

20:23.460 --> 20:24.350
Is it okay?

20:25.000 --> 20:25.590
Okay, okay.

20:25.590 --> 20:26.810
Sure.

20:29.110 --> 20:30.900
It's hard to remember, very tacky.

20:30.900 --> 20:31.810
Well,

20:31.850 --> 20:33.460
besides us, I mean

20:33.680 --> 20:34.720
everyone present,

20:34.720 --> 20:35.920
we will also find some

20:35.920 --> 20:37.050
cross-talk actors,

20:37.110 --> 20:37.880
dancers,

20:38.000 --> 20:38.720
and band

20:38.720 --> 20:39.980
accompanists.

20:40.010 --> 20:41.090
We need to get them all.

20:41.090 --> 20:41.920
Well,

20:42.070 --> 20:44.750
Mr. Ma, let's do this.

20:45.160 --> 20:46.460
For those cross-talk actors

20:46.460 --> 20:47.250
and dancers,

20:47.380 --> 20:49.180
we shouldn't let the benefits
go to outsiders.

20:49.180 --> 20:49.580
Right?

20:49.900 --> 20:51.500
I can do this kind of work too.

20:52.110 --> 20:53.430
If not, I will learn.

20:54.290 --> 20:55.580
We'll put on more shows

20:55.610 --> 20:56.440
and make more money.

20:56.440 --> 20:57.610
Okay, I get what you mean.

20:57.610 --> 20:58.900
That works.

20:59.590 --> 21:00.810
No problem. No problem at all.

21:00.810 --> 21:02.030
Zhuang Zhuang,
you should say something

21:02.030 --> 21:03.030
on this happy occasion too.

21:03.030 --> 21:03.830
I'd better not.

21:03.830 --> 21:04.310
Say a few words.

21:04.310 --> 21:05.070
Go ahead.

21:05.160 --> 21:07.530
You're pretty and sing sweetly.
You must say something.

21:07.530 --> 21:08.010
Okay.

21:09.740 --> 21:10.430
Then let's

21:10.460 --> 21:12.010
unite closely together

21:12.220 --> 21:13.930
for our beautiful future.

21:14.160 --> 21:14.960
Let's do this!

21:15.400 --> 21:17.420
Let's do this!

21:17.420 --> 21:18.470
Cheers!

21:20.920 --> 21:22.380
We founded this art troupe

21:22.640 --> 21:23.910
with a clear goal

21:24.210 --> 21:26.010
of using our talents

21:26.070 --> 21:26.930
to make money.

21:27.050 --> 21:28.360
Because with money,

21:28.460 --> 21:30.470
we can do what we want

21:30.620 --> 21:32.820
and continue to realize our dreams.

21:32.940 --> 21:34.830
Let's go, everyone!

21:34.980 --> 21:37.920
Let's go, let's go!

21:39.680 --> 21:40.970
Our small goal

21:41.050 --> 21:41.990
is to take over

21:42.200 --> 21:44.780
the market in and around Beijing.

21:45.530 --> 21:46.950
Our big goal

21:47.010 --> 21:48.540
is to step out of the country

21:48.610 --> 21:50.520
and aim for the world.

21:50.610 --> 21:53.400
Aim for the world!

21:54.940 --> 21:55.810
Our first stop

21:55.880 --> 21:57.090
is the Spring Planting Conference.

21:56.940 --> 21:58.810
[Singing Along the Way]

21:57.500 --> 21:58.550
The payment they are offering

21:58.550 --> 22:00.120
is quite a lot.

22:00.330 --> 22:01.060
So,

22:01.140 --> 22:02.060
I hope

22:02.180 --> 22:04.880
we can put on a wonderful show.

22:04.990 --> 22:08.330
We must make a great first impression!

22:08.440 --> 22:10.810
Make a great impression!

22:11.330 --> 22:13.060
Make a great first impression.

22:20.500 --> 22:28.950
[Rural Arts Stage]

22:25.480 --> 22:28.070
Dear fellow townsmen,

22:28.590 --> 22:29.750
ladies and gentlemen,

22:29.750 --> 22:30.590
hello, everyone.

22:30.590 --> 22:33.480
Hello!

22:37.040 --> 22:37.770
So handsome.

22:37.810 --> 22:39.980
In this season of revival

22:40.140 --> 22:41.960
and prosperity,

22:42.090 --> 22:44.680
our Singing Along the Way Art Troupe

22:44.740 --> 22:47.240
is very honored to meet you all.

22:47.550 --> 22:50.100
We will use our full enthusiasm

22:50.200 --> 22:51.370
and superb skills

22:51.460 --> 22:54.180
to bring you beauty and happiness.

22:54.250 --> 22:56.460
Nice!

22:57.050 --> 22:59.930
Please enjoy the next dance,

22:58.050 --> 23:00.970
[Rural Arts Stage]

23:00.140 --> 23:01.070
brought to you by

23:01.240 --> 23:04.100
Ranran, Qianqian, Kangkang, and others.

23:04.200 --> 23:06.280
Please give them a warm round of applause!

23:04.820 --> 23:06.560
[Rural Arts Stage]

23:06.310 --> 23:08.610
Alright!

23:10.350 --> 23:11.370
All the best!

23:11.400 --> 23:13.050
All the best!

23:14.850 --> 23:17.200
[Rural Arts Stage]

23:17.480 --> 23:17.900
Start.

24:14.850 --> 24:16.620
Nice!

24:17.140 --> 24:19.600
Encore!

24:19.740 --> 24:23.240
Nice!

24:23.660 --> 24:25.070
Encore!

24:33.180 --> 24:34.380
Nice!

24:34.510 --> 24:35.850
Brothers and sisters,

24:35.940 --> 24:38.070
did you like the performance just now?

24:38.070 --> 24:39.440
Yes.

24:40.310 --> 24:41.240
Good. Now,

24:41.250 --> 24:42.290
I will ask you a question,

24:42.290 --> 24:44.140
and you can only answer with 1 word.

24:44.140 --> 24:46.950
Did they dance well?

24:47.030 --> 24:48.530
Yes!

24:48.530 --> 24:49.440
If we can only say 1 word,

24:49.440 --> 24:50.680
of course, we have to say yes.

24:50.680 --> 24:52.400
They did dance very well.

24:52.440 --> 24:53.610
Everyone liked it, too.

24:53.610 --> 24:54.230
Right?

24:54.460 --> 24:57.200
-He's quite professional.
-But no matter how tasty meat is,

24:57.200 --> 24:58.660
too much of it can get boring.

24:58.660 --> 24:59.270
Right?

24:59.350 --> 25:01.350
We need to try something different.

25:01.520 --> 25:05.050
Now, let's welcome our most beautiful

25:05.180 --> 25:07.110
and talented singer, Zhuang Zhuang,

25:07.110 --> 25:10.220
to bring you a song,
"Flying South."

25:10.250 --> 25:11.070
With supporting dance by

25:11.070 --> 25:14.070
the amateur dance team
of the county cultural center.

25:16.850 --> 25:17.850
Never heard of it.

25:17.940 --> 25:19.070
This song sounds bad.

25:19.070 --> 25:19.800
Yeah.

25:19.960 --> 25:21.090
This song is too old.

25:21.110 --> 25:22.420
It'd be nice to change to some new songs.

25:22.420 --> 25:23.000
Look at this.

25:23.000 --> 25:24.200
The song is too old.

25:24.200 --> 25:25.650
We want to hear new songs.

25:27.180 --> 25:29.640
I'm tired of listening to that song.

25:29.770 --> 25:31.030
I don't want to hear it.

25:42.050 --> 25:45.440
Wild geese are flying south.

25:45.750 --> 25:49.480
Wild geese are flying south.

25:49.480 --> 25:50.200
Get off!

25:50.250 --> 25:58.380
The cries of wild geese break my heart.

25:58.460 --> 26:00.610
The song's too old! Get off the stage!

26:00.660 --> 26:01.590
I don't want to hear it.

26:01.590 --> 26:02.290
Change it.

26:02.400 --> 26:03.700
What... what should we do?

26:03.700 --> 26:04.760
Change the singer!

26:06.900 --> 26:07.460
Well,

26:07.530 --> 26:10.330
dear brothers and sisters,

26:10.440 --> 26:12.140
let me explain.

26:12.920 --> 26:13.970
Our singer

26:14.030 --> 26:15.370
is performing

26:15.510 --> 26:17.170
a professional folk song.

26:17.270 --> 26:18.640
You can only hear this kind of song

26:18.640 --> 26:20.410
on the Spring Festival Gala.

26:20.530 --> 26:22.990
You usually can't hear it
even if you want to.

26:23.290 --> 26:24.280
Can't hear it.

26:25.550 --> 26:26.680
Then how about this?

26:26.700 --> 26:27.850
Everyone, listen to me.

26:27.850 --> 26:28.710
How about this?

26:28.720 --> 26:30.700
Everyone, listen patiently to the end,

26:30.700 --> 26:32.640
then give your judgment after that.

26:32.640 --> 26:33.210
Okay?

26:33.310 --> 26:34.830
Not listening! Not listening!

26:34.830 --> 26:36.630
Not listening, change the song!

26:37.030 --> 26:38.250
Stop singing!

26:38.380 --> 26:39.460
What is this?

26:39.550 --> 26:40.100
This...

26:44.850 --> 26:45.870
Hello, everyone.

26:47.380 --> 26:48.750
I hope you can like

26:48.790 --> 26:50.850
our Singing Along the Way Art Troupe.

26:50.980 --> 26:51.750
How about this?

26:51.750 --> 26:53.840
I'll sing the song

26:53.980 --> 26:55.050
"Yearning" instead.

26:55.050 --> 26:55.830
How does that sound?

26:55.830 --> 26:56.810
Good, that's good.

26:56.810 --> 26:58.140
Good, that song is good.

26:58.180 --> 26:58.640
Okay.

26:59.920 --> 27:01.300
I hope you'll like it.

27:01.460 --> 27:02.120
Good!

27:02.550 --> 27:03.010
Come on.

27:03.480 --> 27:04.480
We know that song.

27:04.510 --> 27:06.640
Exactly, that's a good song.

27:12.720 --> 27:16.400
Where do you come from,

27:17.140 --> 27:20.630
my friend?

27:21.200 --> 27:25.000
Like a butterfly,

27:25.090 --> 27:28.790
flying into my window.

27:29.140 --> 27:36.250
I don't know how many days you can stay.

27:37.090 --> 27:45.030
We've been apart for too long.

27:45.160 --> 27:48.760
Where do you come from,

27:49.070 --> 27:52.940
my friend?

27:53.010 --> 27:55.210
You are like a butterfly,

27:55.240 --> 28:01.220
-flying into my window.
-Nice!

28:01.220 --> 28:05.040
Are you going to

28:05.160 --> 28:09.170
leave in a hurry once more,

28:09.270 --> 28:18.610
and treat the gathering
as a breakup again?

28:20.700 --> 28:24.050
Amazing!

28:24.090 --> 28:25.070
Encore!

28:25.400 --> 28:30.330
Amazing!

28:30.790 --> 28:31.750
Shengli.

28:32.550 --> 28:33.240
What's up?

28:33.440 --> 28:34.340
Here you are.

28:34.590 --> 28:36.040
The village head was

28:36.530 --> 28:38.000
very satisfied.

28:38.090 --> 28:40.160
He said after autumn,

28:40.220 --> 28:41.420
when the harvest is done,

28:41.420 --> 28:42.270
he'll invite us again.

28:42.270 --> 28:43.390
No problem.

28:43.420 --> 28:44.980
We must come back.

28:45.290 --> 28:45.950
For you two.

28:46.160 --> 28:47.220
Okay, thanks, bro.

28:48.850 --> 28:50.050
Zongbao, today was pretty good, right?

28:50.050 --> 28:50.880
For you two.

28:50.970 --> 28:51.970
Thanks, Zongbao.

28:52.240 --> 28:53.240
Thanks, Zongbao.

28:54.160 --> 28:55.290
What are you eating?

28:56.570 --> 28:57.700
Eating, uh, chicken wings.

28:57.700 --> 28:59.100
Why are there 2 portions?

29:00.290 --> 29:01.640
Didn't you sing 2 songs

29:01.640 --> 29:03.240
for the price of 1 today, too?

29:03.960 --> 29:04.860
They said

29:05.050 --> 29:06.400
the response was great.

29:06.770 --> 29:08.310
A lot of people in the audience
are still asking

29:08.310 --> 29:09.380
where they can hear

29:09.400 --> 29:10.160
this girl sing.

29:10.160 --> 29:11.220
They want to hear it.

29:11.220 --> 29:11.940
Liar.

29:13.580 --> 29:15.000
Take your own.

29:16.610 --> 29:18.340
What do you mean yours and mine?

29:18.510 --> 29:19.530
Isn't yours mine,

29:19.530 --> 29:20.720
and mine yours?

29:21.810 --> 29:22.940
Keep it for me first.

29:27.240 --> 29:28.990
Actually, I was worried today.

29:29.050 --> 29:30.650
I was afraid you'd be unhappy

29:31.070 --> 29:32.830
about being forced to change songs

29:32.830 --> 29:34.310
on stage.

29:35.960 --> 29:36.530
No.

29:38.140 --> 29:39.540
Since we're all out here,

29:39.590 --> 29:40.790
we're a team.

29:41.420 --> 29:42.420
I can't cause stage issues

29:42.420 --> 29:43.530
because of me.

29:45.720 --> 29:47.980
I was just worried you'd feel wronged.

29:57.680 --> 29:59.810
We're all just trying to make a living.

30:00.290 --> 30:01.720
And an on-the-spot experience like today

30:01.720 --> 30:03.050
is also very important.

30:04.480 --> 30:05.070
You wouldn't get this opportunity

30:05.070 --> 30:06.270
elsewhere.

30:06.960 --> 30:08.290
I still firmly believe that

30:08.290 --> 30:08.980
there will be a bigger stage

30:08.980 --> 30:10.640
waiting for you in the future.

30:12.440 --> 30:14.050
If anything about our performances

30:14.050 --> 30:15.480
makes you unhappy,

30:15.510 --> 30:16.310
you have to tell me,

30:16.310 --> 30:18.040
and I'll figure something out.

30:21.510 --> 30:22.500
Don't worry.

30:27.830 --> 30:29.210
Since we've started,

30:29.680 --> 30:30.880
we'll give it our all.

30:32.140 --> 30:34.070
We'll be together on this journey.

30:38.240 --> 30:38.720
Okay.

30:52.750 --> 30:54.660
We're finally back around Beijing.

30:54.660 --> 30:55.260
Next stop.

30:55.330 --> 30:56.940
We're performing in the auditorium.

30:56.940 --> 30:57.750
We must express

30:57.750 --> 30:59.240
the style of Singing Along the Way

30:59.240 --> 31:01.440
and the spirit of Singing Along the Way!

31:05.070 --> 31:07.020
[A special performance by
the "Singing Along the Way" Art Troupe]

31:13.580 --> 31:15.780
[A special performance by
the "Singing Along the Way" Art Troupe]

31:17.530 --> 31:20.100
[A special performance by
the "Singing Along the Way" Art Troupe]

31:23.310 --> 31:24.220
It's splendid.

31:33.960 --> 31:36.370
[A special performance by
the "Singing Along the Way" Art Troupe]

31:45.980 --> 31:47.770
Nice!

31:49.850 --> 31:51.510
Nice!

31:52.460 --> 31:53.840
Encore.

31:54.720 --> 31:55.630
Don't go.

31:55.740 --> 31:56.640
You dance so well,

31:56.640 --> 31:57.700
stay at our factory.

31:57.700 --> 31:58.370
Yeah,

31:58.510 --> 31:59.750
you've got a pretty face

31:59.750 --> 32:01.010
and a nice figure.

32:01.240 --> 32:02.570
Do you have a boyfriend?

32:02.590 --> 32:03.410
If not,

32:03.440 --> 32:05.300
I can introduce you to my brother.

32:07.160 --> 32:08.280
Mind your manners.

32:08.330 --> 32:08.870
Sit down.

32:09.750 --> 32:11.210
The next program is called

32:11.270 --> 32:12.920
the Great Illusion.

32:16.440 --> 32:17.980
Nice!

32:18.700 --> 32:19.610
So beautiful.

32:21.700 --> 32:22.850
Really beautiful.

32:22.940 --> 32:24.770
This is the small beauty of our

32:24.810 --> 32:26.670
Singing Along the Way Art Troupe.

32:26.700 --> 32:28.520
With this box,

32:28.680 --> 32:30.840
we will make a big beauty appear.

32:34.070 --> 32:35.600
Those brats just now

32:35.790 --> 32:37.390
were a bit out of line.

32:38.570 --> 32:39.730
But tonight,

32:39.900 --> 32:41.770
we can have a small-scale

32:42.220 --> 32:43.740
gathering with them

32:43.810 --> 32:44.590
right in our factory canteen.

32:44.590 --> 32:45.160
No.

32:45.240 --> 32:46.170
We can't do that.

32:46.510 --> 32:47.670
Yes, yes.

32:48.330 --> 32:49.510
Right, let's arrange it.

32:49.510 --> 32:52.960
3, 2, 1!

32:58.330 --> 32:59.740
Where is this?

33:01.110 --> 33:04.840
This is the
Jianxing Machine Tool Parts Factory.

33:04.940 --> 33:06.100
Great.

33:12.700 --> 33:13.660
Interesting.

33:14.350 --> 33:14.970
Isn't it?

33:15.220 --> 33:16.680
That girl is quite pretty.

33:18.200 --> 33:18.880
What's up?

33:19.070 --> 33:20.130
What are you doing?

33:20.440 --> 33:21.320
Are you lost?

33:21.350 --> 33:23.460
Bro, I was looking for you.

33:23.810 --> 33:24.630
What for?

33:24.920 --> 33:25.920
Here's the thing.

33:26.460 --> 33:27.570
Our factory director

33:27.570 --> 33:28.500
also thinks your performance

33:28.500 --> 33:29.640
is excellent.

33:29.720 --> 33:30.780
You worked so hard.

33:30.920 --> 33:32.650
We want to do our part as hosts.

33:32.740 --> 33:33.330
In a while,

33:33.330 --> 33:35.530
let's have a meal in the factory canteen

33:35.680 --> 33:37.250
and enjoy ourselves a bit more.

33:37.250 --> 33:38.780
We appreciate the gesture.

33:39.090 --> 33:40.330
If you enjoy watching it,

33:40.330 --> 33:42.130
we're happy performing it, too.

33:42.140 --> 33:43.070
But a meal is not necessary.

33:43.070 --> 33:44.000
Not giving face?

33:44.220 --> 33:44.870
No, no.

33:45.250 --> 33:46.600
It's not about face.

33:47.380 --> 33:49.350
We have a performance tomorrow morning.

33:49.350 --> 33:50.700
They already paid the deposit.

33:50.700 --> 33:51.240
After this performance,

33:51.240 --> 33:53.230
we have to rush there overnight.

33:54.090 --> 33:54.640
How much?

33:55.550 --> 33:56.410
We'll pay.

33:56.610 --> 33:57.970
It's not about money.

33:58.000 --> 33:59.180
It's about integrity.

33:59.180 --> 34:00.910
They already paid the deposit.

34:04.030 --> 34:05.230
Please be on your way.

34:09.690 --> 34:10.900
Hey, how about this?

34:11.590 --> 34:13.030
After the performance,

34:13.590 --> 34:15.030
we can take photos together.

34:15.030 --> 34:17.130
Let's take a few more, okay?

34:29.230 --> 34:29.929
Hurry up.

34:30.030 --> 34:31.159
Gather all the boys.

34:31.190 --> 34:32.120
Get more people.

34:32.520 --> 34:34.360
The boss has his eyes on those 2 women.

34:34.360 --> 34:34.880
Keep a close eye on them

34:34.880 --> 34:36.409
and don't let them get away.

34:36.460 --> 34:36.690
Okay.

34:36.690 --> 34:37.510
Especially the lead dancer

34:37.510 --> 34:38.230
and the singer,

34:38.230 --> 34:39.090
Zhuang Zhuang.

34:39.380 --> 34:39.820
Keep a close eye on them.

34:39.820 --> 34:40.480
Don't let them get away.

34:40.480 --> 34:41.679
-Yes, sir.
-Hurry up.

35:10.010 --> 35:12.250
Beat the tambourine and sing a song,

35:12.280 --> 35:15.280
I ride my horse over the mountain slopes.

35:15.340 --> 35:17.610
On the vast grasslands,
cattle and sheep grow strong,

35:17.610 --> 35:20.560
and golden waves
shimmer over the harvest fields.

35:20.610 --> 35:22.930
My tambourine sings heartily,

35:22.960 --> 35:25.890
its joyful singing shakes
the mountains and rivers.

35:25.900 --> 35:28.210
Happy flowers bloom on the grassland

35:28.260 --> 35:30.310
by the hundreds of thousands.

35:34.860 --> 35:36.110
Watch your step.

35:36.280 --> 35:37.230
Watch out.

35:37.280 --> 35:37.980
Slow down.

35:38.460 --> 35:38.960
Zongbao.

35:38.960 --> 35:39.360
What?

35:39.510 --> 35:40.300
When the show is over,

35:40.300 --> 35:41.530
arrange for the others to get on the bus

35:41.530 --> 35:42.360
and leave immediately.

35:42.360 --> 35:44.020
We'll settle the wages later.

35:44.050 --> 35:46.050
No problem. They're all our people.

35:46.070 --> 35:46.900
Tell the rest of us

35:46.900 --> 35:47.840
to pack up our things

35:47.840 --> 35:48.800
and wait for me in the car.

35:48.800 --> 35:49.570
I'll go get the final payment.

35:49.570 --> 35:50.150
After I come back,

35:50.150 --> 35:51.420
we'll leave immediately too.

35:51.420 --> 35:52.820
What's going on?

35:55.960 --> 35:56.440
What?

35:57.690 --> 35:59.770
Okay. I'll go inform them right away.

36:05.390 --> 36:07.350
[Singing Along the Way]

36:07.860 --> 36:09.000
[Singing Along the Way]

36:16.840 --> 36:18.280
Ram your way out!

36:23.300 --> 36:24.760
If I said you couldn't leave,

36:24.760 --> 36:25.960
then you can't leave.

36:26.760 --> 36:27.460
What are you doing?

36:27.460 --> 36:28.720
It's fine. Don't move.

36:29.870 --> 36:31.520
Hey, brothers.

36:31.540 --> 36:33.530
Don't smash the car.

36:33.650 --> 36:34.380
Be careful.

36:34.440 --> 36:36.170
You can smash me instead, okay?

36:36.190 --> 36:37.890
We borrowed this car.

36:37.920 --> 36:38.530
What's the meaning of this?

36:38.530 --> 36:39.500
Open the gate.

36:39.530 --> 36:41.100
Sir, what's going on?

36:41.440 --> 36:42.240
Open the gate?

36:43.670 --> 36:44.980
Is this your territory?

36:44.980 --> 36:46.130
Is this your territory?

36:46.130 --> 36:47.210
No, no, don't.

36:47.280 --> 36:48.690
Bro! Bro!

36:49.400 --> 36:51.100
Listen to me.

36:51.820 --> 36:53.690
We've finished the performance,

36:53.710 --> 36:54.150
right?

36:54.260 --> 36:56.050
We all have each other's numbers, right?

36:56.050 --> 36:58.180
When you come to Beijing in the future,

36:58.730 --> 37:00.030
I'll buy you a drink.

37:00.130 --> 37:02.320
Have a smoke.

37:03.050 --> 37:04.880
I paid a lot of money to invite you here.

37:04.880 --> 37:07.000
You want to leave
before the business is done?

37:07.000 --> 37:08.800
Why is this guy so unreasonable?

37:09.110 --> 37:11.090
You can go wherever you want.

37:11.090 --> 37:11.380
No.

37:11.380 --> 37:12.460
Leave the 2 girls behind.

37:12.460 --> 37:13.130
Don't.

37:14.730 --> 37:15.660
What do you mean?

37:15.800 --> 37:16.530
Don't move.

37:16.550 --> 37:17.880
Or I'll call the police.

37:18.000 --> 37:18.930
Call the police?

37:20.280 --> 37:21.380
Let go!

37:21.400 --> 37:22.250
We're doomed.

37:25.480 --> 37:26.530
What are you doing?

37:26.530 --> 37:27.530
-Go away!
-Scram!

37:27.610 --> 37:28.380
Get away!

37:28.460 --> 37:30.020
Don't touch me!

37:30.090 --> 37:31.610
Let me go! What are you doing?

37:31.610 --> 37:32.280
Let go!

37:32.340 --> 37:33.180
Let go!

37:33.230 --> 37:34.020
Let go!

37:34.460 --> 37:35.190
Are you okay?

37:50.550 --> 37:51.480
Let's see who dares to make a move.

37:51.480 --> 37:52.630
Just try it.

37:52.710 --> 37:53.320
Go ahead.

38:02.390 --> 38:03.940
You were frightened, weren't you?

38:03.940 --> 38:05.870
What matters is that we're unhurt.

38:06.090 --> 38:06.860
I didn't expect to encounter

38:06.860 --> 38:09.000
such a thing on a performance tour.

38:09.050 --> 38:10.920
If the police hadn't arrived in time,

38:10.920 --> 38:11.960
we'd have been helpless.

38:11.960 --> 38:12.760
You're right.

38:13.690 --> 38:15.150
None of us expected it.

38:15.590 --> 38:16.510
But no matter what,

38:16.510 --> 38:17.440
as the director,

38:18.230 --> 38:20.360
I want to apologize to everyone first.

38:21.920 --> 38:23.120
When you're out and about,

38:23.120 --> 38:24.920
you can meet all kinds of people.

38:24.980 --> 38:25.980
It's very normal.

38:26.060 --> 38:26.450
Tell me,

38:26.450 --> 38:28.650
what would you do if this happens again?

38:29.000 --> 38:31.000
If the police hadn't arrived in time

38:31.020 --> 38:32.250
and controlled the situation this time,

38:32.250 --> 38:33.510
wouldn't we have been done for?

38:33.510 --> 38:34.820
We have ladies in our group, too.

38:34.820 --> 38:36.670
Should we prepare some tools?

38:37.100 --> 38:38.500
Well,

38:38.740 --> 38:40.650
let me say a few words.

38:40.970 --> 38:43.350
Recently,

38:43.380 --> 38:45.840
everyone has indeed worked hard.

38:46.160 --> 38:48.030
But we've made good money, too.

38:48.060 --> 38:48.740
Right?

38:49.190 --> 38:49.800
If it really doesn't work out,

38:49.800 --> 38:51.590
let's take a break for a while.

38:51.780 --> 38:53.510
Our Singing Along the Way trope

38:53.580 --> 38:55.840
needs to rest and recharge.

38:55.860 --> 38:56.700
Right?

38:57.760 --> 38:58.660
Right.

38:58.680 --> 39:00.240
It wasn't our fault this time.

39:00.240 --> 39:02.100
We should carry on as usual.

39:02.390 --> 39:04.310
Let's have a good meal.

39:05.840 --> 39:07.860
Yes, carry on as usual.

39:07.990 --> 39:09.920
Don't take everything to heart.

39:10.100 --> 39:11.840
We'll eat, drink, and chat

39:11.860 --> 39:14.080
to our heart's content.

39:14.880 --> 39:16.200
That's right.

39:16.230 --> 39:16.790
Right?

39:17.130 --> 39:18.250
Right, Zhuang Zhuang?

39:18.250 --> 39:18.970
Yes.

39:19.230 --> 39:20.240
It's no big deal.

39:20.270 --> 39:21.520
It's no big deal.

39:24.140 --> 39:25.480
Finally back in Beijing.

39:25.480 --> 39:26.340
Give me a smile.

39:27.110 --> 39:28.230
I can't smile.

39:28.590 --> 39:30.510
You were terrified just now, weren't you?

39:30.510 --> 39:31.690
I was scared to death.

39:31.690 --> 39:33.220
I'm still reeling even now.

39:34.160 --> 39:35.810
My arm was pulled so hard it hurts.

39:35.810 --> 39:37.470
How about I massage it for you?

39:38.070 --> 39:39.210
I learned how.

39:39.240 --> 39:40.580
-No need.
-It’s like playing the saxophone.

39:40.580 --> 39:41.090
Let me massage it for you.

39:41.090 --> 39:42.690
It'll swell even more later.

39:45.140 --> 39:45.660
Ranran,

39:50.340 --> 39:51.940
I have something to give you.

39:52.270 --> 39:53.290
What is it?

39:55.550 --> 39:56.090
Ranran.

39:58.080 --> 39:59.170
Wait a moment.

40:06.240 --> 40:11.380
[Luogu Hutong]

40:07.230 --> 40:08.560
Why are you here?

40:08.580 --> 40:09.740
I've been calling you these past few days.

40:09.740 --> 40:10.620
Why didn't you answer?

40:10.620 --> 40:11.550
Where did you go?

40:11.870 --> 40:14.130
I was on a performance tour with friends.

40:16.620 --> 40:17.260
Ranran,

40:17.360 --> 40:18.000
if you haven't had

40:18.000 --> 40:18.770
any acting roles recently,

40:18.770 --> 40:19.670
You could have told me.

40:19.670 --> 40:21.120
I'd have figured something out.

40:21.120 --> 40:22.650
Why are you running performances?

40:22.650 --> 40:24.320
Isn't it just a waste of time?

40:25.410 --> 40:26.940
Are you here for something?

40:27.260 --> 40:28.440
There is a project.

40:28.460 --> 40:29.820
The director has his eyes on you

40:29.820 --> 40:30.750
after he watched

40:30.750 --> 40:31.640
your performance in

40:31.640 --> 40:32.800
"Golden Garden at Sunset."

40:32.800 --> 40:35.590
This is a big project.
Opportunities like this are rare.

40:35.590 --> 40:36.250
Tonight,

40:36.280 --> 40:37.560
the producer and the director
have a dinner party.

40:37.560 --> 40:38.430
Hurry up and come with me.

40:37.770 --> 40:39.820
[Luogu Hutong]

40:45.060 --> 40:46.370
Do I have to go today?

40:48.570 --> 40:50.650
It's now or never.

40:50.960 --> 40:51.920
Your call.

41:03.780 --> 41:04.520
Liangliang,

41:04.770 --> 41:06.210
Mr. Chu told me

41:06.400 --> 41:07.470
there's a big project,

41:07.470 --> 41:08.860
and he wants me to give it a try.

41:08.860 --> 41:11.360
The director and people from the studio
will be there.

41:11.360 --> 41:12.750
Have dinner without me.

41:12.880 --> 41:14.460
Can you tell Zhuang Zhuang for me?

41:14.460 --> 41:16.680
Okay, I'll let them know.

41:16.840 --> 41:18.300
I'll get going then.

41:18.760 --> 41:19.280
Bye.

41:21.440 --> 41:23.260
[Luogu Hutong]

41:50.230 --> 41:53.180
Wild geese are flying south.

41:53.260 --> 41:56.580
Wild geese are flying south.

41:57.190 --> 42:03.360
The cries of wild geese break my heart.

42:03.440 --> 42:05.280
Stop singing.

42:05.360 --> 42:06.280
What's with you now?

42:06.280 --> 42:07.430
What are you up to?

42:07.500 --> 42:08.900
The finalist list is out.

42:08.980 --> 42:09.590
It's out?

42:10.210 --> 42:12.690
Look! You made it to the finals!

42:11.610 --> 42:12.070
[National Singer Competition
Organizing Committee]

42:12.090 --> 42:12.790
[Notice of participation
in the National Singer Competition]

42:14.380 --> 42:15.830
That's splendid.

42:16.080 --> 42:18.010
[Notice of participation
in the National Singer Competition]

42:18.070 --> 42:20.070
Zhuang Zhuang, congratulations.

42:20.170 --> 42:20.840
You are now

42:20.840 --> 42:22.650
getting closer and closer to your dream.

42:22.650 --> 42:23.880
Stay composed.

42:23.880 --> 42:24.590
You must keep your composure.

42:24.590 --> 42:25.090
At this point,

42:25.090 --> 42:26.260
your mindset is the most important.

42:26.260 --> 42:27.460
Eat well, sleep well,

42:27.480 --> 42:28.650
and prepare for the competition.

42:28.650 --> 42:30.570
Practice more and take more classes.

42:30.570 --> 42:31.630
Isn't it only a few months away?

42:31.630 --> 42:31.890
Yes.

42:31.900 --> 42:33.360
Arrange more classes for Zhuang Zhuang.

42:33.360 --> 42:34.110
For free, okay?

42:34.110 --> 42:36.280
-It’s free. It’s definitely free.
-I’ll ask her mom

42:36.280 --> 42:37.280
to make a few more outfits for me

42:37.280 --> 42:37.940
instead.

42:37.980 --> 42:39.780
So that's what you're thinking.

42:40.000 --> 42:41.260
Thank you, Mrs. Zheng.

42:41.320 --> 42:42.300
Thank you, Mr. Zheng.

42:42.300 --> 42:43.160
Zhuang Zhuang.

42:45.070 --> 42:46.310
I wish you success,

42:46.710 --> 42:48.440
and that your dream comes true.

42:50.050 --> 42:50.500
Okay.

42:52.010 --> 42:52.460
All the best!
